V0601_01_00_00_0.text:
Very well.
I accept your challenge!

V0601_01_00_01_0.text:
I'll Duel to the final card.
And I will be victorious!

V0601_01_00_02_0.text:
This Duel won't be easy.
I must Duel at my very best to win!

V0601_01_00_03_0.text: Are you sure you can win this, Playmaker?

V0601_01_00_03_1.text:
Never doubt me, Ai.
Let's go!

V0601_01_00_04_0.text:
Keep on your toes, Playmaker!
This is gonna be tough!

V0601_01_00_04_1.text:
I know.
But I can't afford to lose!

V0601_01_00_05_0.text: Just cuz that meatbag's your friend, don't go easy on him!

V0601_01_00_05_1.text: I never take Soulburner lightly - not if I want to win.

V0601_01_00_06_0.text:
It's The Gore!
What deck ya think he's playing with this time?

V0601_01_00_06_1.text:
It doesn't matter.
As long as I can outstrategize him!

V0601_01_00_07_0.text:
Be careful!
I heard she's a superstar in LINK VRAINS!

V0601_01_00_08_0.text:
Varis!
I will stop at nothing to defeat you!

V0601_01_00_09_0.text:
Aagh! Not her!
She's the sneakiest sneak to ever sneak!

V0601_01_00_10_0.text:
Knight of Hanoi!
You’ll be seeing a lot more of me.

V0601_01_00_10_1.text:
So you ought to remember my name.
It's Playmaker!

V0601_03_00_00_0.text: I've already linked the circuit to victory!

V0601_03_00_01_0.text: I must stay focused to the very end!

V0601_03_00_02_0.text:
Oooooooh.
Is this one of those free wins?

V0601_03_00_02_1.text:
Stay alert - it's never that easy.
It's my turn!

V0601_03_00_05_0.text:
My tingles are tingling!
Be careful!

V0601_03_00_06_0.text: This match is far from over!

V0601_03_00_07_0.text: I will get the card I need!

V0601_05_00_00_0.text: This draw is for the fate of the future!

V0601_07_09_00_0.text: I'll flip over the card that I set!

V0601_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0601_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0601_16_00_01_0.text: I'll bring this Duel to an end!

V0601_21_00_01_1.text:
Any clue what they're gonna do?
Nothing by the looks of it.

V0601_21_00_02_0.text:
I thought this Duel'd be easy - and I was right!
Hahahaha!

V0601_21_00_02_1.text:
Never underestimate your opponent!
I end my turn!

V0601_21_00_04_0.text: That brings my turn to an end!

V0601_21_00_05_1.text: You know they're gonna come at you hard, right?

V0601_21_00_06_0.text: No matter how dire it gets, I never give up!

V0601_21_00_08_1.text: It'd be nice if you decide to START PLAYING BETTER!

V0601_28_00_01_0.text: My Cyberses were the key to my success!

V0601_28_00_02_0.text: One wrong step and I would've lost this Duel.

V0601_28_00_03_0.text:
You may have many tactics, but I have Ai.
And that’s enough!

V0601_28_00_04_0.text: Don't be ashamed for losing a well-fought fight.

V0601_28_00_04_1.text:
Why not!?
You humans are weird.

V0601_28_00_05_0.text:
Woohoo!
You won, Playmaker!
You ol' meatbag you!

V0601_28_00_07_0.text: The memories of my friends were what pushed me to win.

V0601_28_00_08_0.text: Each small bond built towards our common goal of victory!

V0601_33_00_01_0.text: This is the only move to escape this situation!

V0601_33_00_02_0.text: I'm calculating the formula for victory!

V0601_33_00_04_1.text:
Sure am, my dude!
I'm whipping up a Data Storm!

V0601_33_00_05_0.text: I’ve updated your Skill to make it even more powerful!

V0601_33_00_05_2.text:

Neo Storm Access!

V0601_30_00_00_0.text: I don't recall asking for your opinion.

V0601_30_00_02_0.text: I'm not a Duelist to take lightly.

V0601_34_00_00_0.text: This is not the kind of Duel I want.

V0601_34_00_01_0.text: Hmm... I think you have a different plan in mind...

V0601_34_00_02_0.text: There are three reasons why I must win this Duel.

V0601_34_00_03_0.text: One: I can sense your strong desire to win this Duel.

V0601_34_00_04_0.text: Two: You want both of us to enjoy this Duel.

V0601_34_00_05_0.text: Three: Therefore, it'd be an honor to win a Duel like this!

V0601_34_00_09_0.text: I have no clue what you're doing.

V0601_34_00_10_0.text:
Too late now!
You've fallen for our combo!

V0601_34_00_11_0.text:
That deck's tough.
Not sure if you can wiiiiin.

V0601_34_00_12_0.text: My processing processors process every process!
